      <title>葛蘭素史克就 Covid-19 疫苗技術起訴輝瑞和 BioNTech</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/glaxosmithkline-sues-pfizer-biontech-over-covid-19-vaccine-technology-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葛蘭素史克週四在特拉華州聯邦法院起訴輝瑞和 BioNTech，指控它們侵犯了葛蘭素史克與這兩家公司的重磅新冠疫苗中的信使 RNA (mRNA) 技術相關的專利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/glaxosmithkline-sues-pfizer-biontech-over-covid-19-vaccine-technology-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 13:40:07 GMT</pubDate>
